---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Enfoque Retail y Mayoristas | EMRG" description="Acompañamos a pequeños negocios en su salto digital. Tu primera web, visibilidad en Google y captación de clientes.">
  
  <section class="scene active" id="scene-0">
    <div class="hero-block-imm">
      <p class="label-imm">Digitalización Local</p>
      <h1 class="title-imm">El Salto <br/><span class="teal-glow">Digital.</span></h1>
      <p class="desc-imm">Si tu negocio no aparece en Google, no existe online. Ayudamos a pequeños negocios a crear su página web, aparecer en mapas y empezar a captar clientes.</p>
      
      <div class="action-grid-imm">
        <a href="#scene-3" class="btn-imm" onclick="window.goToScene(3); return false;">Solicita Diagnóstico //</a>
        <div class="metric-chip-imm">
           <span class="m-val-imm">MAPS SYNC</span>
           <span class="m-val-imm">FIRST WEB</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="scene" id="scene-1">
    <div class="content-wrap-imm">
      <h2 class="section-title-imm">El Riesgo: <span class="teal-glow">Inexistencia Digital.</span></h2>
      
      <div class="pillars-imm">
        <div class="pillar-box-imm">
          <span class="p-num-imm">01</span>
          <h3>Oscuridad Local</h3>
          <p>Clientes cercanos encuentran a tu competencia en el mapa antes que a ti.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-box-imm">
          <span class="p-num-imm">02</span>
          <h3>Brecha de Credibilidad</h3>
          <p>Sin una web propia que explique quién eres, el cliente duda de tu servicio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-box-imm">
          <span class="p-num-imm">03</span>
          <h3>Techo de Crecimiento</h3>
          <p>Dependencia exclusiva del boca a boca sin un canal de captación 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="scene" id="scene-2">
    <div class="content-wrap-imm">
      <h2 class="section-title-imm">Nuestros <span class="teal-glow">Paquetes Prácticos.</span></h2>
      <div class="services-imm">
         <div class="service-row-imm">
            <span>01</span>
            <h3>Presencia Inicial</h3>
         </div>
         <div class="service-row-imm">
            <span>02</span>
            <h3>Impulso Local Ads</h3>
         </div>
         <div class="service-row-imm">
            <span>03</span>
            <h3>Soporte Estratégico</h3>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="scene" id="scene-3">
    <div class="content-wrap-imm">
      <div class="contact-split-imm">
        <div class="contact-text-imm">
          <h2 class="section-title-imm">Quiero mi <span class="teal-glow">Diagnóstico.</span></h2>
          <p class="desc-imm">Evaluamos tu visibilidad actual y te mostramos cómo dar el primer paso online.</p>
        </div>
        
        <form class="imm-form retail-form">
          <div class="form-row-imm">
            <input type="text" placeholder="NOMBRE" required />
            <input type="text" placeholder="NEGOCIO" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row-imm">
            <input type="text" placeholder="RUBRO" required />
            <input type="text" placeholder="CIUDAD" required />
          </div>
          <textarea placeholder="¿CUÁL ES TU OBJETIVO?" required></textarea>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-imm">Solicitar Diagnóstico //</button>
          <p class="success-imm" style="display:none; margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--teal); font-weight: 800;">MENSAJE ENVIADO. REVISAREMOS TU CASO.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-wrap-imm {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .label-imm {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: block;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .title-imm {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-family: var(--title);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .section-title-imm {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    font-family: var(--title);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .teal-glow {
    color: var(--teal);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--teal-dim);
  }

  .desc-imm {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--smoke);
    max-width: 550px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .action-grid-imm {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .btn-imm {
    background: var(--teal);
    color: #000;
    padding: 18px 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: 0.3s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--body);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .btn-imm:hover {
    background: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .metric-chip-imm {
     display: flex;
     gap: 20px;
     font-size: 0.75rem;
     color: var(--teal);
     font-family: monospace;
     font-weight: 800;
  }

  .pillars-imm {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pillar-box-imm {
    padding: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rim);
    background: var(--surface);
    transition: 0.3s;
  }

  .pillar-box-imm:hover {
    border-color: var(--teal);
  }

  .p-num-imm {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: block;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .pillar-box-imm h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-family: var(--title);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .services-imm {
     width: 100%;
  }

  .service-row-imm {
     display: flex;
     align-items: center;
     gap: 48px;
     padding: 32px 0;
     border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rim);
     transition: 0.3s;
  }

  .service-row-imm:hover {
    padding-left: 24px;
    border-bottom-color: var(--teal);
  }

  .service-row-imm span {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .service-row-imm h3 {
     font-size: 3.5rem;
     font-family: var(--title);
     text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .contact-split-imm {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 80px;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .imm-form {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rim);
  }

  .form-row-imm {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  input, textarea {
    background: var(--void);
    border: 1px solid var(--rim);
    padding: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--body);
  }

  textarea {
    height: 120px;
    resize: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pillars-imm, .contact-split-imm, .form-row-imm {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const form = document.querySelector('.retail-form');
    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        form.reset();
        const success = form.querySelector('.success-imm');
        if (success) success.style.display = 'block';
      });
    }
  });
</script>
